Package za.ac.wits.elen4010.fluidsim.gui

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    DataPoint
    Standard interface for a data point in the program.
    InteractivePanel
    Defines an interface for all interactive panels in the program.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DataNode
    The data node acts as the lowest level of the heirarchy for the TimeCapture class.
    DataPanel
    The data panel is designed specifically to capture data in the form of DataPoints from the Java standard MouseListener and MouseMotionListener interfa- ces
    DataProcessor
    Buffers data during an execution of the data capture phase of the program.
    FileReader<T>
    Respondible for streaming objects from a file to a super process to use them for some purpose.
    FileWriter<T>
    Responsible for accepting objects and printing them to the output file specified.
    GraphicalPanel
    The GraphicalPanel handles the rendering of the simulation by reading the input file via the FileReader which streams RawFrames to the main program which contain the float matrices necessary to display the density output graphically on the screen
    GUI
    The GUI is the main class of the program and is designed to be able to spawn all of the different components of the application.
    LabelNode
    The label node acts as the highest level of the hierarchy for the TimeCapture class.
    MenuPanel
    The Menu panel is designed to allow the user to change the state of the program between capture a- nd render through the DataPanel and GraphicalPanel respe- ctively.
    RawFrame
    Container class for the output of the simulation.
    SamplePoint
    SamplePoint acts as a simple data storage device to allow for enhanced communication between the DataPanel and DataProcessor modules.
    SimulationInput
    Container class for the input of the simulation.
    TimeCapture
    A logging class which ensures synchronised logging and logging for different identifiers of two heirarchical levels.
    Velocity
    Simple storage object designed to carry velocity information
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    GUI.loadedFileType
    The file type which was determined using the determineFileType() function
    MenuActions
    Enumeration type for Menu options
